it.csi.mddtools.guigen

Interface WebResourceModule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    StdWebResourceModule

    public interface WebResourceModule
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Web Resource Module'. Modulo di risorse web che l'applicazione utilizza in vario modo. Preferibilmente si utilizza la sottoclasse StdWebResourceModule.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Version
    • Deployment Type
    • Repart Module
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getWebResourceModule()
